    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Deciduous shrub common to the Mediterranean region whose gray-green rush-like shoots are used in basket-making and provide a fiber employed in products as cords, coarse cloth, and canvas.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
